# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Rust & Cargo
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Compiled outputs and build directories (matches anywhere in the tree)
target/

# Cargo backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these debugging information files
*.pdb

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cargo.lock Handling
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# For a Cargo workspace, you typically want a single `Cargo.lock` at the 
# root and you *should* commit it. 
# If you have independent crates (not a workspace) and they are libraries, 
# you might want to ignore their lockfiles. Uncomment if needed:
# Cargo.lock

